Description: Vulture is an HTTP reverse proxy with authentication and filtering features
 Vulture is an HTTP reverse proxy. It does many security checks
 (authentication, rewriting, filtering...) before proxying requests
 from Internet to your web applications. With authentication
 enabled, vulture will provide Web-SSO to users. With embedded
 ModSecurity firewall engine, it can prevent web attacks such 
 as Cross Site Scripting and SQL Injection.
